data.description: This spacious updated 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom pool home in the heart of the exclusive Isles at Bayshore community is waiting for you. Large pool and the backyard with palms along the perimeter is beautifully lit. Open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the expansive kitchen and family room. The oversized master bedroom offers a private sanctuary, complete with en-suite bathroom and generous closet space. Amenities including 24-hour security, a state-of-the-art fitness center, extra large Olympic size swimming pool with spa, entertainment room, room for celebrating events, playground, and more. With a VERY LOW HOA fee , this community offers luxury living. 5 minutes from the renowned Blackpoint Marina, easy access to boating, fishing and Black Creek Trail, easy access to main roads.
